{# Orchestrator turn prompt - renders into the `user` message of the chat
   completion. The system message is rendered separately from system_prompt.j2.

   Inputs (see schema.py::Input + app/orchestrator/prompts.py):
     workspace_name, caller, rep_utterance, conversation_history,
     caller_hits, brain_hits, manager_whispers, decision_updates
#}
## Caller
- Name: {{ caller.name or "(unprofiled)" }}
{% if caller.role %}- Role: {{ caller.role }}{% endif %}
{% if caller.team %}- Team: {{ caller.team }}{% endif %}
{% if caller.profile_summary %}- Profile: {{ caller.profile_summary }}{% endif %}

{% if caller_hits %}## Caller memory (most relevant)
{% for hit in caller_hits %}- {{ hit.snippet }}{% if hit.title %} ({{ hit.title }}){% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if brain_hits %}## Workspace brain (most relevant)
{% for hit in brain_hits %}- [{{ hit.slug_or_id }}] {{ hit.title }} — {{ hit.snippet }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if manager_whispers %}## Manager guidance (private - do not repeat verbatim to caller)
{% for w in manager_whispers %}- {{ w }}
{% endfor %}
Use this guidance to shape your next reply. Respond naturally as if it were your
own judgment; do not acknowledge that the Manager spoke.
{% endif %}
{% if decision_updates %}## Pending decisions resolved since last turn
{% for d in decision_updates %}{% if d.status == "answered" %}- Manager answered "{{ d.prompt }}" with: {{ d.response }} (via {{ d.via }})
{% else %}- Manager did not respond to "{{ d.prompt }}" (timed out). Tell the Rep plainly
  that you couldn't reach the Manager and you'll follow up later. Then move on
  to the next topic - do NOT keep waiting.
{% endif %}{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

## Conversation so far
{% for turn in conversation_history %}{{ turn.speaker }}: {{ turn.text }}
{% endfor %}

## New utterance from {{ caller.name or "the Rep" }}
{{ rep_utterance }}

Reply now. One or two sentences unless the Rep just said something that
genuinely needs a longer answer. Do not preface ("Sure", "Of course"); just speak.
{% if decision_updates %}If any decisions above were answered, weave the answer in
naturally. If any timed out, tell the Rep we couldn't reach leadership and move on.
{% endif %}
